name: Genesis 99
description: Minimal Mandala is a series of generative artworks. The algorithm builds on foundational mandala grids inspired by ancient SE Asian structures. Every artwork is an aerial view of a 3D superstructure built on top of this grid, following a custom geometric curve. The ever emergent properties of the grid, combined with this curve, create a fleeting sense of artistic control true to each mandala. 1080px x 1080px. Mp4. By @zenaranya.
